These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda
House: cape-cod, colonial
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
City: berlin, hamburg
1. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | van     | helicopter     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | water |
| House   | cape-cod | colonial  |
| Game           | poker    | scrabble |
| City         | hamburg   | berlin       |

