.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
House: art-deco, colonial
There 2 different types of food: potato, peach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person eating potato is the art-deco house##1
3. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Game      | poker    | scrabble |
| House           | colonial  | art-deco     |
| Food   | peach       | potato      |
| Flower           | daffodil        | rose      |
| Transport         | scooter | jet-ski     |

