.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, documentary
There 2 different types of food: pear, lettuce
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog
1. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the dog##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage         | 7up     | iced-tea    |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery     | documentary |
| Food   | lettuce    | pear   |
| Flower         | poppy | sunflower   |
| Pet     | rabbit | dog |

