.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, white
House: modern, tower
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Flower          | bellflower     | lily     |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | pony        |
| Hobby   | filmmaking      | fishing         |
| Color   | white | amber       |
| House         | modern  | tower |

