The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, punk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, rugby
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, vegafina
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, video-games
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
